Title: Bullet to the Head Official Trailer #1 (2012) - Sylvester Stallone Movie HD
Comment: Just finished watching this on a DVD I picked up from a thrift store on Nebraska Ave., Tampa, Florida.  And on special, too.  25% off from $1.75.  Wednesday.  Old fogey's day.  Not a bad deal, considering.  This is latter-day Walter Hill.  An aged Pro fondly looking back.  I was in my early 20's when I saw his early action-cut holler jobs. "Hard Times". "The Driver".  "The Warriors".  Classic genre movies with a single vision.  The best against the bad.  Later on the scope got broader: "The Long Riders", "Southern Comfort", "48 hours", "Streets of Fire".  Afterwards,  it was all mostly blink-n-flash.  This one, "Bullet to the Head", is quite decent, done with lots of style.  Good buy.  No big complaints.  A nit: Sly shoulda worn a beaten-up brown leather jacket.
